org.codice.ddf.catalog.async.processingframework.api.internal

Interface ProcessingFramework


  • public interface ProcessingFramework

    This code is experimental. While this interface is functional and tested, it may change or be removed in a future version of the library.

    The ProcessingFramework processes all requests submitted to it. A Request is converted to the appropriate data recognized by the ProcessingFramework. Available requests for processing are as follows:

    • ProcessRequest
